title: The current buffer is not necessarily displauyed in Emacs.
pid: 23933641-348f-4311-b1c8-a14aa708c8e1
body: |2-
  https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/manual/html_node/elisp/Current-Buffer.html
  It is just the one that Lisp functions target.
  `current-buffer` returns it.
  `set-buffer` changes it.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
